This project uses ai-scaffold. The single source of truth is
`.ai/AI_CONTEXT.md`; always follow the rules in `.ai/rules/`.

When asked to run a skill by name, open and follow the matching playbook (if it
is installed):

- `adr-write` → `.ai/skills/context/adr-write.md`
- `ai-init` → `.ai/skills/ai-init.md`
- `ai-log-write` → `.ai/skills/context/ai-log-write.md`
- `context-update` → `.ai/skills/context/context-update.md`
- `debug` → `.ai/skills/debug.md`
- `incident` → `.ai/skills/incident.md`
- `migration` → `.ai/skills/migration.md`
- `new-endpoint` → `.ai/skills/new-endpoint.md`
- `pr-review` → `.ai/skills/workflow/pr-review.md`
- `pr-write` → `.ai/skills/workflow/pr-write.md`
- `refactor` → `.ai/skills/refactor.md`
- `review` → `.ai/skills/review.md`
- `security-review` → `.ai/skills/security-review.md`
- `task-implement` → `.ai/skills/workflow/task-implement.md`
- `task-plan` → `.ai/skills/workflow/task-plan.md`
- `test-gen` → `.ai/skills/test-gen.md`
- `ticket-clarify` → `.ai/skills/workflow/ticket-clarify.md`
- `verify` → `.ai/skills/workflow/verify.md`
